										li: a.comment-classic-reply(href='#' aria-label='reply')

							.comment-classic-group
								// Comment Classic
								article.comment-classic
									figure.comment-classic-figure: +img('comment-02-48x48').comment-classic-image
									.comment-classic-main
										p.comment-classic-name Albert Webb
										.comment-classic-text
											p Fuga observares, tanquam placidus bubo. Ubi est mirabilis nix? Cum classis favere, omnes ollaes resuscitabo altus, clemens exsules. Ignigena altus adelphis est.
